1.0.name: wordpress/innhand-reservation-system
1.0.description:
Use innHand plugin to embed our internet reservation system in to your wordpress site.

The Internet reservation system, also called online booking engine, allows your guests to make online reservations on the web site of your property. More info at http://www.innhand.com/features/internet-reservation-system.html
